                    <p id="point2" style="font-size: 20px;">
                        Since the beach is a ever changing environment, it can be dangerous to ones who are unaware of the potential hazards. Safety signs and flags are put in place to aware/warn us about ongoing or permanent hazards that are present at the beaches. You should always look out for the beach safety sign board before you step into waters at any beach.
