                    <div class="row">

                        <div class="col-md-5">
                            <img src="~/images/AquaticLife/AquaticLife6.jpg" width="100%" height="100%">

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-7">
                            <p><b>Sharks-</b> Australian coastline is famous for the sharks but do not worry, most of them are harmless to humans. But still, seeing one brings fear.</p>

                            <b style="font-size: 20px;">
                                Some quick tips to avoid or minimize the chances of encountering a shark at beach-
                            </b>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    Always look for the warning signs before entering into the waters.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Try to avoid swimming at dawn and dusk.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Try to avoid swimming at river mouths and discoloured waters.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Try to avoid swimming in or around the waters which is pool for baitfish.
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                        </div>

